they backed it up with something else.

00:18:45.310 --> 00:18:48.290
So there's a checkmark on the green,
correct answers,

00:18:48.350 --> 00:18:52.150
and there's an X on the red,
incorrect answers.

00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:56.400
Another thing that you
want to keep in mind,

00:18:56.660 --> 00:18:59.570
especially if you're
embedding video in your books,

00:18:59.570 --> 00:19:01.810
