00:35:48.760 --> 00:35:50.670
this thing is a dialogue.

00:35:50.790 --> 00:35:52.700
So let's talk about how to use it.

00:35:52.700 --> 00:35:56.390
First of all,
we're going to assign semantic roles.

00:35:57.250 --> 00:36:02.610
So on the front of this planet
widget or solar system widget,

00:36:02.610 --> 00:36:05.860
we have the sun and the
moon and ten planets,

00:36:05.860 --> 00:36:08.600
