00:38:15.340 --> 00:38:18.890
And likewise, when we hide that dialogue,
we want to focus the trigger element

00:38:18.890 --> 00:38:20.440
or the element that it came from.

00:38:20.480 --> 00:38:24.130
So they click the moon button and
